WEBVTT

00:11.959 --> 00:13.502
Everything about football inspires me.

00:13.669 --> 00:14.549
Being on the pitch is best,...

00:14.687 --> 00:15.690
...but I also love to watch it.

00:17.806 --> 00:19.410
My mom introduced football to me.

00:19.666 --> 00:21.971
That's why I train hard every day...

00:22.134 --> 00:23.118
...to make her proud.

00:24.417 --> 00:27.469
World Cup superstars inspire me.

00:30.039 --> 00:31.768
I don't score goals, I save them.

00:31.989 --> 00:34.658
Imagine stopping the winning goal of the World Cup final.

00:36.212 --> 00:38.915
I like to wow people when I play football.

00:40.124 --> 00:43.181
Being part of a team pushes me to chase my dreams.

00:51.817 --> 00:54.401
KIA, movement that inspires.

